<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُّحْدَثٍ}</span> ... حَدِيثِ التَّنْزِيلِ يُجَدِّدُ الذِّكْرَى لَهُمْ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَسَرُّوا النَّجْوَى}</span> ... بَالَغُوا فِي إِخْفَاءِ مَا يَتَنَاجَوْنَ بِهِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَضْغَاثُ أَحْلَامٍ}</span> ... أَخْلَاطُ مَنَامَاتٍ لَا حَقِيقَةَ لَهَا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{جَسَدًا}</span> ... أَجْسَادًا خَارِجَةً عَنْ طِبَاعِ البَشَرِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فِيهِ ذِكْرُكُمْ}</span> ... فِيهِ عِزُّكُمْ، وَشَرَفُكُمْ، إِنِ اتَّعَظْتُمْ بِهِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَكَمْ قَصَمْنَا}</span> ... كَثِيرًا أَهْلَكْنَا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَحَسُّوا}</span> ... رَأَوْا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَاسَنَا}</span> ... عَذَابَنَا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَرْكُضُونَ}</span> ... يُسِرِعُونَ هَارِبِينَ مِنَ العَذَابِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أُتْرِفْتُمْ}</span> ... نُعِّمْتُمْ فِيهِ فَبَطِرْتُمْ وَاسْتَكْبَرْتُمْ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَا وَيْلَنَا}</span> ... يَا هَلَاكَنَا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَصِيدًا}</span> ... كَالزَّرْعِ المَحْصُودِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَامِدِينَ}</span> ... مَيِّتِينَ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَقْذِفُ بِالْحَقِّ}</span> ... نَرْمِي بِهِ، وَنُبَيِّنُهُ فَنَرُدُّ بِهِ البَاطِلَ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَيَدْمَغُهُ}</span> ... يَمْحَقُهُ، وَيَدْحَضُهُ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{زَاهِقٌ}</span> ... ذَاهِبٌ، مُضْمَحِلٌّ.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>